A vintage 1980s-style illustration of an anxious person sitting at a wooden desk in dim evening lamplight, staring at an old laptop computer displaying an ominous blue screen. Wisps of smoke or heat waves rise dramatically from the laptop's vents. The room has warm amber tones contrasting with the cold blue glow of the failing screen. On the desk, scattered technical manuals and a coffee cup sit untouched. Through a window behind, a dusky purple Sunday evening sky with a setting sun. The illustration uses muted earth tones with pops of warning orange and distressed blue, rendered in a nostalgic magazine advertisement style with visible halftone dots and slightly faded colors.
